Smart focus settings let you capture breathtaking macro images with ease, while an ingenious remote control feature uses another device’s camera to set up natural-looking selfies, group shots, and even videos. With one-touch editing, optional captions, and stylish filters to choose from, Camera Plus is also fantastic for adding the finishing touches to your pictures.
